node.title: Soft Color
node.description: Shot taken at Magnolia Gardens in Charleston, SC.  Believe it or not, I did not do much editing in lightroom to get this final image.  Added some clarity and contrast, but this was whatI saw in camera.  Got lucky with the way the light caught this one.
